  "name": "JOURYOKU (STRENGTH RANK)",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<table><caption>Table 1-6: Strength Ranks</caption><thead><tr><th>Strength Rank</th><th>Combat</th><th>Actions</th><th>Carry</th><th>Ignore Hardness</th><th>Damage Reduction</th><th>Cost</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>1</td><td>+1</td><td>-</td><td>-</td><td>-</td><td>-</td><td>1 / 5 rounds</td></tr><tr><td>2</td><td>+1</td><td>+2</td><td>x1.5</td><td>2</td><td>-</td><td>2 / 5 rounds</td></tr><tr><td>3</td><td>+2</td><td>+4</td><td>x2</td><td>4</td><td>-</td><td>3 / 5 rounds</td></tr><tr><td>4</td><td>+2</td><td>+6</td><td>x2</td><td>6</td><td>-</td><td>4 / 5 rounds</td></tr><tr><td>5</td><td>+3</td><td>+8</td><td>x2.5</td><td>8</td><td>-</td><td>1 / round</td></tr><tr><td>6</td><td>+4</td><td>+10</td><td>x2.5</td><td>8</td><td>2</td><td>3 / 2 rounds</td></tr><tr><td>7</td><td>+4</td><td>+10</td><td>x3</td><td>8</td><td>3</td><td>2 / round</td></tr><tr><td>8</td><td>+5</td><td>+11</td><td>x3</td><td>8</td><td>5</td><td>5 / 2 rounds</td></tr><tr><td>9</td><td>+5</td><td>+11</td><td>x3.5</td><td>8</td><td>6</td><td>3 / round</td></tr><tr><td>10</td><td>+6</td><td>+12</td><td>x4</td><td>10</td><td>8</td><td>5 / round</td></tr></tbody></table><p>In addition to the benefits as shown below, Strength Ranks permanently increase your carrying capacity as though your Strength were increased by 1 per Strength Rank you have obtained.</p><p><strong>Combat:</strong> You roll attack and weapon damage as though your Strength modifier was increased by this amount.</p><p><strong>Actions:</strong> This bonus applies to Climb, Jump, and Swim checks, as well as Disarm, Trip, Grapple, Bull Rush and Overrun checks. It also applies to Strength checks.</p><p><strong>Ignore Hardness:</strong> You may ignore an object's hardness if its hardness is equal to or lower than this number.</p><p><strong>DR:</strong> You gain this Damage Reduction, which can be overcome by Dark Iron.</p>",
